      "description": "This E46 M3 represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated Bavarian engineering. Under the hood, the S54B32 straight-six remains in pristine mechanical state, featuring meticulously maintained individual throttle bodies and a fully serviced double VANOS system. The Getrag 420G six-speed manual gearbox offers crisp, short-throw engagement, channeling power to the rear wheels through the factory variable M-differential lock. The chassis is structurally flawless, with proactive subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings throughout, ensuring the original kinematic precision is preserved. Every seal, gasket, and fluid line is factory-spec, presenting a turn-key example for the discerning collector who demands mechanical perfection and high-revving performance.",
